Month = {{OCT}},
Abstract = {{Industry 4.0 or industrial Internet of things (IIoT) has become one of
   the most talked-about industrial business concepts in recent years.
   Thus, to efficiently integrate Internet of things technology into
   industry, the collected and sensed data from IIoT need to be scheduled
   in real-time constraints, especially for big factories. To this end, we
