Abstract = {{Representing real world objects as digital models has been a central
   topic of computer science for many years. However, in order to reduce
   the complexity and owing to the memory and processing limitations of IT
   devices, the digital models have always been quite tightly focused.
   Digital Twins (DT) are about to change this. The DT concept conveys the
   idea that digital representations should possess many of the essential
   properties of their real-world counterparts along their whole lifetime
