   as an initiative to increase industrial added value is based on
   establishing connectivity between CPS and to enable communication
   between CPS. The industrial application scenarios for Industrie 4.0 aim
   at vertical and horizontal life-cycle integration concepts where digital
   twin technology plays an important role. This contribution explains
   major concepts of Industrie 4.0 and derives the role of digital twin
