   innovative environmentally sustainable solution is proposed for the
   fashion apparel manufacturing industry (FAMI), which is energized by
   blockchain. Incorporating the Emission Trading Scheme (ETS), and a novel
   ``emission link{''} system, the proposed framework exposes carbon
   emission to the public and establishes a feature to reduce the emissions
   for all key steps of clothing making. Fully compatible with Industry
   4.0, blockchain provides decentralization, transparency, automation, and
   immutability characteristics to the proposed framework. Specifically,
   the blockchain supported ETS framework, the carbon emissions of clothing
   manufacturing life cycle, and the emission link powered procedures are
