   automated warehouses. Travel-time model that considers the real
   operating characteristics of the shuttle carrier and the elevator's
   lifting table, has been used. Assuming uniform distributed storage
   locations and the probability theory, expressions for the expected cycle
   time of the elevator's lifting table and the shuttle carrier have been
