   series of new challenges to the traditional Enterprise Information
   Systems (EIS). More and more networked manufacturing entities are
   combined with data sensing, collection, transmission, and actuation
   capabilities. EIS are now facing large amounts of heterogeneous data. To
   address this issue, this paper proposes a notification-oriented solution
   for the data-intensive EIS within a distributed, collaborative, and
   heterogeneous environment. The solution is then applied in terms of
