Abstract = {{Current industry must improve the day-to-day control and industrial
   communications of its processes in order to bring itself closer to the
   Industry 4.0 paradigm. To attain these improvements, which aim towards
   obtaining agile and intelligent manufacturing systems, the IEC-61499
   standard is considered to be the main option by many researchers.
